content.rendered:
Directed by Vishal Bhardwaj.

Written by Matthew Robbins. Sabrina Dhawan. Vishal Bhardwaj. Vishal Bhardwaj.

Cast Kangana Ranaut(Julia). Shahid Kapoor(Nawab Malik). Saif Ali Khan(Rusi Billimoria). Manav Vij(Bhyro Singh). Ujjwal Chopra(Major P.K. Sehgal). Kuldeep Sareen(Col. Shahnawaz Khan). Saharsh Kumar Shukla(Zulfi (as Saharsh Shukla)). Rushad Rana(Hoshang Billimoria). Shriswara Dubey(Haseena). Gajraj Rao(Ahuja). Pooja Sarup(Bulbul). Atul Kumar(Chulbul). Richard McCabe(Major General Harding). Alex Avery(Major Williams). Surendra Pal(Raja). Amruta Khanvilkar(Rani). Nitant Shrivastava(Rusi’s Manager). Gerson Da Cunha(Bappawa (as Gerson D’Cunha)). Barzin(Firdaus). Neel(Cyrus). Kashmira Irani(Zenobia). Lin Laishram(Mema). Satoru Kawaguchi(Hiromichi (as Kawaguchi Satoru)). Ballu Panchal(Mema’s son (as Ballu A. Panchal)). Taku Koging(Mule man). Sunidhi Chauhan(Self (In Song Bloody Hell)). Tsukasa Kadota(Japanese Soldier). Pankaj Kumar(Director). Aalaap Majgavkar(Rusi’s Editor). Nitesh Pandey(Patel). Umair Patel(Musical Artist (archive sound)). Bhawsheel Sahni(Jamadar Hukam Singh (as Bhawsheel Singh Sahni)). Shriswara(Haseena). Edward Sonnenblick(Officer)

Languages Hindi. English.

Producers Rekha Bhardwaj. Vishal Bhardwaj. Ollwyn Dsouza. Gundeep Kohli. Rakesh Madhotra. Vikas Mehta. Sajid Nadiadwala. Akshay Powale. Sandeep Sharma. Joga Singh. Anshul Talwar.

Production Viacom18 Motion Pictures. Vishal Bhardwaj Pictures. Nadiadwala Grandson Entertainmens.
